73
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,600
People say
weird things happened in our house.

74
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:09,700
Some even say I run my shops

75
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:11,060
through demonic power.

76
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,720
I'm Heavenly Lord Dacheng,

77
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,650
an immortal from the Nine Heavens,

78
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,880
and those mortals
are actually calling me a demon.

79
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,820
Ridiculous.

80
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:24,120
Heavenly Lord Dacheng, don't be mad.

81
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,640
How about I cook for you tonight
to make it up to you?

82
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,640
What do you think?

83
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,930
You can cook?

84
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,920
I learned it from Madam Yang.

85
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,380
What would you like to eat?

86
00:05:38,010 --> 00:05:39,010
What can you make?

87
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:44,710
Snow fungus soup with rock sugar,
rib broth with bitter melon,

88
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:47,480
and barley soup
with wax gourd and seaweed.

89
00:05:48,450 --> 00:05:49,970
Why are they all soups?

90
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,380
Soups help clear heat.

91
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,409
You've been irritable lately.

92
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:55,300
