for about 20 years, haven't you?

168
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:13,240
My Lady,

169
00:13:14,060 --> 00:13:16,820
it's been exactly 22 years.

170
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:20,040
I remember when you first got here,

171
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,290
you didn't even reach my shoulder.

172
00:13:21,290 --> 00:13:23,440
Now even your son
is almost taller than me.

173
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:26,110
Yes, Huaiyu's growing fast.

174
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:28,130
He's grown much taller lately.

175
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,340
That's wonderful.

176
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:31,860
Take this.

177
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,440
Sorry, My Lady,

178
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:44,220
I cannot accept this.

179
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:47,280
Huaiyu's a smart, hardworking boy.

180
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:49,980
He shouldn't stay here
and waste his potential.

181
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:53,160
Use the money to buy a house outside,

182
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,820
and find him a proper school.

183
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,010
With his potential,

184
00:13:58,520 --> 00:14:00,600
I believe he'll make something of himself.

185
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,340
And you won't need
to worry about money anymore.

186
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:04,140
Just enjoy the rest of your life.

187
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:11,440
My Lady, I'm grateful for your offer,

188
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:12,320
but…

189
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:15,450
Since the day you saved me,

190
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:17,360
my life has belonged to you.

191
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:20,980
I swore before the statue
of Primordial God

192
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,440
to serve you my whole life

193
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,720
and be loyal to you until the end.

194
00:14:28,690 --> 00:14:31,540
I'm doing great.
I don't need looking after.

195
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,650
I don't need your service anymore.

196
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,770
There's no need for you to stay.

197
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:40,440
My Lady.

198
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,080
Please let me stay!

199
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,420
My Lady!

200
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:28,640
I'll be away for a while.

201
00:16:29,050 --> 00:16:30,640
If you truly wish to stay,

202
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,320
then help me keep watch over Qichi Hall.

203
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,320
Yes, My Lady.

204
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:46,900
Then I'm leaving it to you, Steward Meng.

205
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:03,150
[Qichi Hall]

206
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:10,440
Master loves peace and quiet.

207
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:13,290
Once your work is done,

208
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,810
stay in your rooms and rest.

209
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,760
Don't wander around.

210
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,880
Especially, do not enter Master's room.

211
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:31,320
Also, during winter,
Master loves sweet potatoes.

212
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:35,830
Make sure to take good care of
the sweet potato field in the backyard.

213
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,910
Water and fertilize it on time.

214
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:41,250
Don't slack off, not even for a day.

215
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:42,340
Yes.

216
00:18:43,710 --> 00:18:44,510
Steward Meng,

217
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:47,320
I heard your grandson
is a government official.

218
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:49,480
Why are you still here taking orders

219
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,310
as a servant?

220
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:51,400
Wouldn't it be better

221
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:53,440
to leave this place
and enjoy a luxurious life

222
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,440
with your family?

223
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:02,480
Master doesn't like gossipy people.

224
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,710
Neither do I.

225
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,080
If you're staying here,

226
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:09,110
speak less and work more.

227
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:10,760
Understood.

228
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:12,880
Steward Meng.

229
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:14,580
A letter from your family.

230
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,290
A letter from my family?

231
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:26,070
It's from my grandson.

232
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:51,910
[To my grandfather Meng Chi]

233
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,020
My Lady.

234
00:21:05,480 --> 00:21:07,720
It's so late. What's the matter?

235
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:20,840
I have a grandson—

236
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,720
the one working as an official.

237
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:27,920
I've just heard
he's been charged with something,

238
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:31,080
and in a few days, he'll be executed.

239
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:33,640
I know that boy.

240
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:37,640
He's been pure and kind
since he was little.

241
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:40,070
He'd never do anything bad.

242
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:44,400
There has to be some mistake.

243
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,120
My Lady.

244
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:50,620
I know you're not an ordinary person.

245
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:52,920
Please…

246
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,080
