247
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:00,120
Help him, please.

248
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,340
Everything happens for a reason.

249
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:17,640
Even I cannot interfere with it.

250
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:39,640
